			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Origin moment for Minsc + Jaheira with Boss Friol.&#xD;&#xA;After Minsc learns of the Zhentarim plans to overthrow Nine-Fingers, he returns to the Guildhall to confront their leader, Roah. She taunts him with his past evil deeds as the 'Stone Lord' - the player decideds whether to back Minsc and fight Roah, or let Roah's plan come to fruition for the 'greater good'." />
